{"tid":2305184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［反攻中國］廣東惠州新增1無症狀感染者　自香港經深圳灣口岸入境","createTime":"2020-11-29T12:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T05:27:40.000Z","uid":290118,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"93ebc2d46ee0c0d4154712b78e8d09294181d174","tid":2305184,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"XG01唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n據廣東省衛健委通報稱，11月28日，全省無新增確診病例，新增境外輸入無症狀感染者2例，廣州報告1例，來自尼日利亞；惠州報告1例，來自中國香港，以上均在隔離點發現，入境後即被隔離觀察。<br />\n<br />\n而根據惠州衛健局微信號發布信息，11月28日0&mdash;24時，惠州市報告1例境外輸入無症狀感染者，在集中隔離醫學觀察場所發現。<br />\n<br />\n惠州衛健局指，該無症狀感染者為男性，中國籍，從香港經深圳灣口岸入境抵惠，入境後按全程閉環管理程序轉運至集中隔離醫學觀察場所，後轉至定點醫院觀察治療，目前情況穩定。"},{"pid":"47aa64786d7ef44174a26fdfb0aa218752f577f3","tid":2305184,"uid":276273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yiftogF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyiftogF.jpg&h=e669b808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"835b5269359760b2a6b6a90c7eef5102a6662574","tid":2305184,"uid":32028,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"一個中國呀，咩香港輸入呀<br />\n惠州係咪支持港獨"},{"pid":"24c6be142b2f376a60087d0c9649981549c08c19","tid":2305184,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎同胞共享肺炎榮耀<br />\nOn99 自己假清零仲咁多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20435d2ed519f20b2d683c564967244f07adba59","tid":2305184,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"渣油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c18fdccc4aeb5f884ac831e6a952f64c9b13942","tid":2305184,"uid":44454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"有晚見到B3X成半車人， 真係唔明嗰啲係咩人， 可以隨便過關， 有個仲帶住手帶"},{"pid":"92fea4cb50307e70a2eeaeca